        "Defines RagRequest Pydantic model: doc_ids, question, top_k, language",
        "Proxies to external IDIRS service at configurable base URL (default localhost:8010)",
        "RAG endpoint calculates confidence score from non-zero chunk scores",
        "RAG endpoint uses RAG_CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD to determine high/low confidence",
        "RAG endpoint builds Gemini prompt with retrieved chunks, answer, and confidence score",
        "Supports bilingual responses (de/en) in RAG analysis",
        "Error handling: 504 for timeout, 503 for connection error, upstream status for HTTP errors",
        "Uses logging module for warning on Gemini analysis failures",
        "Falls back to raw RAG answer if Gemini analysis fails"
      ]
    },
